#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the documentation for the &kde; &systemsettings; module that "
"configures graphic tablets."
msgstr ""
"To je dokumentacija za &kde; &systemsettings; modul, ki konfigurira grafične "
"tablice."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "System Settings"
msgstr "Sistemske nastavitve"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wacom"
msgstr "Wacom"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>Tablet</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>Tablični računalnik</keyword>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wacom Tablet Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve tablice Wacom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tablet &systemsettings; module handles all setting for your graphic "
"tablet. All tablets supported by the <ulink url=\"https://linuxwacom.github."
"io\">&Linux; Wacom driver</ulink> project are handled by this settings "
"interface. Make sure your tablet is detected either via xorg.conf or udev "
"and works in general. Refer to the <link linkend=\"detection\">tablet "
"detection</link> section for more information."
msgstr ""
"Tablični računalnik &systemsettings; modul obravnava vse nastavitve za vašo "
"grafično tablico. Vsi tablični računalniki, ki jih podpira <ulink url="
"\"https://linuxwacom.github.io\">&Linux; Projekt gonilnika Wacom</ulink> "
"upravlja ta nastavitveni vmesnik. Prepričajte se, da je vaš tablični "
"računalnik zaznan prek xorg.conf ali udev in da na splošno deluje. Za več "
"informacij glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"detection\">zaznavanje tabličnega "
"računalnika</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <application>xf86-input-wacom</application> driver must be installed on "
"your computer and <command>xsetwacom</command> must be available in order to "
"make this module work correctly."
msgstr ""
"Gonilnik <application>xf86-input-wacom</application> mora biti nameščen v "
"vašem računalniku in <command>xsetwacom</command> mora biti na voljo, da bo "
"ta modul deloval pravilno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The module is split into various tab pages that handle all aspects of your "
"tablet and the pen: <link linkend=\"tablet-profiles\">Profiles</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"tablet-general\">General Information</link>, <link linkend=\"stylus"
"\">Stylus Settings</link>, <link linkend=\"pad-buttons\">Express Buttons</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"pad-mapping\">Pad Mapping</link> and <link linkend="
"\"touch-mapping\">Touch Mapping</link>."
msgstr ""
"Modul je razdeljen na različne strani z zavihki, ki obravnavajo vse vidike "
"tabličnega računalnika in peresa: <link linkend=\"tablet-profiles\">Profili</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"tablet-general\">Splošne informacije</link >, <link "
"linkend=\"stylus\">Nastavitve pisala</link>, <link linkend=\"pad-buttons"
"\">Hitri gumbi</link>, <link linkend=\"pad-mapping\">Preslikava ploskve</"
"link> in <link linkend=\"touch-mapping\">Preslikava dotika</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Profile Management"
msgstr "Upravljanje profilov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the small drop down box with the two buttons next to it. You can "
"create new profiles and delete already existing ones. Each profile is saved "
"and specified for the currently connected tablet. If you create a new "
"profile, it automatically creates one with the default settings as returned "
"by the driver."
msgstr ""
"To je majhno spustno polje z dvema gumboma poleg njega. Ustvarite lahko nove "
"profile in izbrišete obstoječe. Vsak profil je shranjen in določen za "
"trenutno povezano tablico. Če ustvarite nov profil, se samodejno ustvari "
"profil s privzetimi nastavitvami, ki jih vrne gonilnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can specify different profiles for your settings. For example if "
"you like to have a different behavior of the pen when you use it as a mouse "
"replacement for your day to day work or using it as pen to draw something."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite različne profile za svoje nastavitve. Na primer, če "
"želite imeti drugačno obnašanje pisala, ko ga uporabljate kot nadomestek "
"miške za vsakodnevno delo ali ga uporabljate kot pisalo za risanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each profile can be changed on the fly and directly changes the behavior of "
"your tablet input."
msgstr ""
"Vsak profil je mogoče spremeniti sproti in neposredno spremeni vedenje vnosa "
"tabličnega računalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"kded\">kded tablet daemon</link> must be running in the "
"background to be able to change the profiles and apply them to the tablet. "
"All the work is done by the daemon. The &systemsettings; module just change "
"the profile settings for it."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kded\">Demon tabličnega računalnika kded</link> mora "
"delovati v ozadju, da lahko spremenite profile in jih uporabite za tablični "
"računalnik. Vse delo opravi demon. &systemsettings; modul samo spremenite "
"nastavitve profila zanj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Tablet Settings and Information"
msgstr "Splošne nastavitve tabličnega računalnika in informacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows some general Information about the detected tablet. Beside the name "
"and company of your tablet an image is shown and all detected input devices "
"are listed."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže nekaj splošnih informacij o zaznani tablici. Poleg imena in podjetja "
"vašega tabličnega računalnika je prikazana slika in navedene so vse zaznane "
"vhodne naprave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tablet must be connected and the <link linkend=\"kded\">kded</link> must "
"be running to allow the module to work correctly."
msgstr ""
"Tablični računalnik mora biti povezan in <link linkend=\"kded\">kded</link> "
"mora delovati, da omogoči pravilno delovanje modula."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the <link linkend=\"troubles\">Detection problems</link> section for "
"further help on the tablet detection."
msgstr ""
"Glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"troubles\">Težave z zaznavanjem</link> za "
"dodatno pomoč pri zaznavanju tabličnega računalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the tablet information the general tab allows to set various "
"global shortcuts. Each shortcut allows to dynamically change the options for "
"the current connected tablet."
msgstr ""
"Poleg informacij o tabličnem računalniku zavihek splošno omogoča nastavitev "
"različnih globalnih bližnjic. Vsaka bližnjica omogoča dinamično spreminjanje "
"možnosti za trenutno povezano tablico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stylus Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve pisala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pen that is used together with the tablet has two different sides, the "
"main side is called stylus the other end is the eraser. In this tab you can "
"change any aspect of the pen from the button assignment to the pressure "
"curve and threshold."
msgstr ""
"Pero, ki se uporablja skupaj s tablico, ima dve različni strani, glavna "
"stran se imenuje pisalo, drugi konec pa je radirka. V tem zavihku lahko "
"spremenite kateri koli vidik peresa od dodelitve gumba do krivulje pritiska "
"in praga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eraser Feel"
msgstr "Občutek radirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The slider allows to alter the threshold of the eraser. For a more fine "
"grained setting of the pressure it is possible to alter the complete "
"pressure curve in the <guilabel>Edit Pressure Curve</guilabel> dialog. See "
"<link linkend=\"presscurve\">Press Curve Dialog</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Drsnik omogoča spreminjanje praga radirke. Za natančnejšo nastavitev "
"pritiska je možno spremeniti celotno krivuljo pritiska v pogovornem oknu "
"<guilabel>Uredi krivuljo tlaka</guilabel>. Za več informacij glejte <link "
"linkend=\"presscurve\">Pogovorno okno Krivulja pritiska</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve gumba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Button Settings</guilabel> box allows to alter the executed "
"action assigned to each button of the pen. A simple click into the edit box "
"opens a new dialog where different key combinations, modifier keys and mouse "
"buttons can be selected."
msgstr ""
"Polje <guilabel>Nastavitve gumbov</guilabel> omogoča spreminjanje izvedenega "
"dejanja, dodeljenega vsakemu gumbu peresa. Preprost klik v polje za urejanje "
"odpre novo pogovorno okno, kjer lahko izberete različne kombinacije tipk, "
"modifikacijske tipke in gumbe miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Tap to execute action</guilabel> is enabled the stylus must be "
"in contact with the tablet in order to allow the button action to be "
"executed. If this option is disabled each button action works also when the "
"stylus is hovering above the tablet."
msgstr ""
"Če je <guilabel>Dotaknite se za izvedbo dejanja</guilabel> omogočeno, mora "
"biti pisalo v stiku s tablico, da se omogoči izvajanje dejanja gumba. Če je "
"ta možnost onemogočena, vsako dejanje gumba deluje tudi, ko pisalo lebdi nad "
"tablico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tip Feel"
msgstr "Občutek vrha pisala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The slider allows to alter the threshold of the stylus tip. For a more fine "
"grained setting of the pressure it is possible to alter the complete "
"pressure curve in the <guilabel>Edit Pressure Curve</guilabel> dialog. See "
"<link linkend=\"presscurve\">Presscurve Dialog</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Drsnik omogoča spreminjanje praga konice pisala. Za natančnejšo nastavitev "
"tlaka je možno spremeniti celotno krivuljo tlaka v pogovornem oknu "
"<guilabel>Uredi krivuljo pritiska</guilabel>. Za več informacij glejte <link "
"linkend=\"presscurve\">Pogovorno okno Krivulja pritiska</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Express Buttons"
msgstr "Hitri gumbi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Express Buttons</guilabel> tab allows to set specific button "
"actions for all hardware buttons for the tablet. To change the used action, "
"you need to click into the edit box and choose the action in the new dialog."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Hitri gumbi</guilabel> omogoča nastavitev posebnih dejanj "
"gumbov za vse gumbe strojne opreme tabličnega računalnika. Če želite "
"spremeniti uporabljeno dejanje, morate klikniti v polje za urejanje in "
"izbrati dejanje v novem pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Tablet</title>"
msgstr "<title>Tablični računalnik</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Tablet</guilabel> tab allows to set further properties of the "
"tablet area when used together with a pen. In here the orientation of the "
"tablet area, valid space of the used tablet and the cursor tracking mode can "
"be specified."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Tablet</guilabel> omogoča nastavitev nadaljnjih lastnosti "
"območja tablice, kadar se uporablja skupaj s peresom. Tukaj je mogoče "
"določiti usmerjenost območja tablice, veljaven prostor uporabljene tablice "
"in način sledenja kazalcu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stylus Tracking Mode"
msgstr "Način sledenja pisalu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Map to Screen</guilabel> : This mode maps the pen cursor with "
"absolute movement to the tablet. The edges of the tablet represent directly "
"the space of the screen."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preslikaj na zaslon</guilabel> : Ta način preslika kazalec peresa "
"z absolutnim gibanjem na tablico. Robovi tablice predstavljajo neposredno "
"prostor zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Map to Cursor</guilabel> : This mode maps the pen cursor with "
"relative movement to the tablet."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preslikaj v kazalec</guilabel> : Ta način preslika kazalec peresa "
"z relativnim premikanjem v tablico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Orientation"
msgstr "Orientacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The orientation box specifies how the tablet area is rotated. You can set a "
"specific rotation on your own in the combobox or if you enable the "
"<guilabel>Auto-Rotate with Screen</guilabel> option, the tablet will "
"automatically rotated together with the screen. This is done by listening to "
"the xrandr events when the screen is rotated."
msgstr ""
"Polje za usmerjenost določa, kako se območje tablice zasuka. Določen zasuk "
"lahko nastavite sami v kombiniranem polju ali če omogočite možnost "
"<guilabel>Samodejno zasukaj z zaslonom</guilabel>, se bo tablica samodejno "
"zasukala skupaj z zaslonom. To se naredi s poslušanjem dogodkov xrandr, ko "
"se zaslon zasuka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have problems with the autorotation option and the tablet is always "
"rotated into the wrong direction, enable the <guilabel>Invert Auto-Rotation</"
"guilabel> option to invert this."
msgstr ""
"Če imate težave z možnostjo samodejnega zasuka in je tablica vedno zasukana "
"v napačno smer, omogočite možnost <guilabel>Obrni samodejno zasuk</"
"guilabel>, da to obrnete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tablet Mapping"
msgstr "Preslikava tabličnega računalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mapping allows to specify the proportions of the tablet that will be "
"used for each screen. This is necessary to keep the tablet area proportional "
"to the used screen space in absolute stylus tracking mode. For more "
"information check the <link linkend=\"area-selection\">Area Selection "
"Dialog</link> section."
msgstr ""
"To preslikavo omogoča določitev razmerja tablice, ki bo uporabljena za vsak "
"zaslon. To je potrebno, da je površina tablice sorazmerna z uporabljenim "
"prostorom na zaslonu v absolutnem načinu sledenja pisalu. Za več informacij "
"si oglejte razdelek <link linkend=\"area-selection\">Pogovorno okno za "
"izbiro območja</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209 index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option does not work for relative cursor mode."
msgstr "Ta možnost ne deluje v načinu relativnega kazalca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Touch"
msgstr "Dotik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Touch</guilabel> tab allows to set further properties for the "
"touch part of the tablet (if available). It is possible to disable the touch "
"feature via the <guilabel>Enable Touch</guilabel> check box. Also a global "
"shortcut exist that allows to enable/disable the touch feature."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Dotik</guilabel> omogoča nastavitev dodatnih lastnosti za "
"del tablice na dotik (če je na voljo). Funkcijo dotika je mogoče onemogočiti "
"s potrditvenim poljem <guilabel>Omogoči dotik</guilabel>. Obstaja tudi "
"globalna bližnjica, ki omogoča omogočanje/onemogočanje funkcije dotika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Touch Tracking Mode"
msgstr "Dotaknite se načina sledenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Map to Screen</guilabel> : This mode maps the touch cursor with "
"absolute movement to the tablet. The edges of the tablet represent directly "
"the space of the screen."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preslikaj na zaslon</guilabel> : Ta način preslika kazalec na "
"dotik z absolutnim gibanjem na tablico. Robovi tablice predstavljajo "
"neposredno prostor zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Map to Cursor</guilabel> : This mode maps the touch cursor with "
"relative movement to the tablet."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preslikaj v kazalec</guilabel> : Ta način preslika kazalec na "
"dotik z relativnim premikanjem v tablico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gestures"
msgstr "Kretnje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Enable Gestures</guilabel> is enabled, the tablet can generate "
"gesture events for the touch device."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno <guilabel>Omogoči poteze</guilabel>, lahko tablični "
"računalnik ustvari dogodke potez za napravo na dotik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Scroll Distance</guilabel> : Allows to scroll through windows when "
"two fingers are placed on the tablet, moving them up/down creates a scroll "
"event. The Distance is given in tablet units."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razdalja drsenja</guilabel> : Omogoča drsenje po oknih, ko na "
"tablico položite dva prsta; premikanje ju gor/dol ustvari dogodek drsenja. "
"Razdalja je podana v enotah tablice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Zoom Distance</guilabel> : Allows to zoom in/out by moving two "
"fingers together or apart from each other. The Distance is given in tablet "
"units."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razdalja povečave</guilabel> : Omogoča povečavo/pomanjšanje s "
"premikanjem dveh prstov skupaj ali narazen. Razdalja je podana v enotah "
"tablice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Tap Time</guilabel> : This time in milliseconds specifies when a "
"double tap on the device is recognized as right-click"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Čas dotika</guilabel> : ta čas v milisekundah določa, kdaj je "
"dvojni dotik naprave prepoznan kot desni klik"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Touch Mapping"
msgstr "Dotaknite se Preslikave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mapping allows to specify the proportions of the touch device that will "
"be used for each screen. This is necessary to keep the tablet area "
"proportional to the used screen space in absolute stylus tracking mode. For "
"more information check the <link linkend=\"area-selection\">Area Selection "
"Dialog</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Ta preslikava omogoča določitev razmerja naprave na dotik, ki bo uporabljena "
"za vsak zaslon. To je potrebno, da je površina tablice sorazmerna z "
"uporabljenim prostorom na zaslonu v absolutnem načinu sledenja pisalu. Za "
"več informacij si oglejte razdelek <link linkend=\"area-selection"
"\">Pogovorno okno za izbiro območja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press Curve Dialog"
msgstr "Pritisnite pogovorno okno Krivulja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the Press Curve dialog"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Krivulja pritiska"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the press curve"
msgstr "Spreminjanje krivulje pritiska"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The press curve defines how the pressure of the stylus is translated. The "
"press curve is defined via four points of a Bézier curve. To change this "
"curve you can alter the red dots and move the curve around."
msgstr ""
"Krivulja pritiska določa, kako se prevede pritisk pisala. Krivulja pritiska "
"je definirana s štirimi točkami Bézierove krivulje. Če želite spremeniti to "
"krivuljo, lahko spremenite rdeče pike in premaknete krivuljo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use your pen inside the press curve dialog to see the changes in the press "
"curve directly. A blue area below the curve shows the applied pressure of "
"the pen."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite pero v pogovornem oknu krivulje stiskanja, da si neposredno "
"ogledate spremembe krivulje stiskanja. Modro območje pod krivuljo prikazuje "
"pritisk peresa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Area Selection Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za izbiro območja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the Tablet Area Dialog"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna območja tabličnega računalnika"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defining the Tablet Area"
msgstr "Določanje območja tablice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows to specify the available tablet area for each selected "
"screen space. In order to keep the aspect ratio of the tablet it is "
"necessary to reduce the tablet area depending on the screen resolution. This "
"Dialog allows to specify them for each screen individually."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko določite razpoložljivo površino tablice za vsak "
"izbrani prostor na zaslonu. Da bi ohranili razmerje med višino in širino "
"tablice, je potrebno zmanjšati površino tablice glede na ločljivost zaslona. "
"V tem pogovornem oknu jih lahko določite za vsak zaslon posebej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Toggle Screen</guilabel> button to switch between "
"fullscreen (all connected monitors) and each individual monitor. The "
"settings will be saved for each screen configuration and applied to the "
"tablet whenever the screen selection is switched by the global shortcut "
"action."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guilabel>Preklop zaslona</guilabel> za preklop med "
"celozaslonskim (vsi povezani monitorji) in posameznim monitorjem. Nastavitve "
"bodo shranjene za vsako konfiguracijo zaslona in uporabljene v tabličnem "
"računalniku vsakič, ko bo izbira zaslona preklopljena z dejanjem globalne "
"bližnjice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to map the screen with the <guimenuitem>Full Tablet</"
"guimenuitem> area or just defined <guimenuitem>Tablet Area</guimenuitem> on "
"the <guilabel>Tablet</guilabel> pane rightwards. The proportions of the area "
"can be locked or unlocked using the <guibutton>Lock proportions</guibutton> "
"switch button."
msgstr ""
"Zaslon je mogoče preslikati z območjem <guimenuitem>Celotna tablica</"
"guimenuitem> ali samo določenim <guimenuitem>Območje tablice</guimenuitem> v "
"podoknu <guilabel>Tablet</guilabel> desno. Razmerja območja lahko zaklenete "
"ali odklenete s preklopnim gumbom <guibutton>Zakleni razmerja</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to keep the aspect ratio of the tablet with the current screen "
"selection you can press the <guilabel>Set Screen Proportions</guilabel> "
"button. The tablet area will be calculated and changed automatically."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ohraniti razmerje stranic tabličnega računalnika s trenutno izbiro "
"zaslona, lahko pritisnete gumb <guilabel>Nastavi razmerja zaslona</"
"guilabel>. Površina tablice bo samodejno izračunana in spremenjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition you can open the <guilabel>Calibrate</guilabel> dialog to "
"calibrate your tablet with the help of four points on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko odprete pogovorno okno <guilabel>Umerjanje</guilabel> za "
"umerjanje tablice s pomočjo štirih točk na zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the dialog is closed, the last selected screen will be used. If you "
"want to switch the screen later on, you can use the <link linkend=\"tablet-"
"general\">Global Shortcut</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je pogovorno okno zaprto, bo uporabljen zadnji izbrani zaslon. Če želite "
"zaslon pozneje preklopiti, lahko uporabite <link linkend=\"tablet-general"
"\">Globalno bližnjico</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tablet area only works for absolute tracking mode of the touch and pen "
"cursor device. In relative mode the full tablet is used."
msgstr ""
"Območje tabličnega računalnika deluje samo v načinu absolutnega sledenja "
"naprave s kazalcem na dotik in pero. V relativnem načinu se uporablja "
"celotna tablica."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tablet daemon"
msgstr "Demon tabličnega računalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tablet daemon runs in the background and does the ground work. Detecting "
"the tablet and set it up with the selected profiles. If the daemon is not "
"running the &systemsettings; module and the plasma applet cannot work "
"properly and the tablet cannot be used with the profiles."
msgstr ""
"Demon tabličnega računalnika deluje v ozadju in opravlja osnovno delo. "
"Zaznavanje tablice in nastavitev z izbranimi profili. Če demon ne izvaja "
"&systemsettings; modul in plasma programček ne moreta pravilno delovati in "
"tabličnega računalnika ni mogoče uporabljati s profili."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tablet detection"
msgstr "Zaznavanje tabličnega računalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The detection of the <hardware>tablet device</hardware> is done in several "
"ways. <application>Solid</application> is used in the first step and does "
"the hotplug support. If Solid fails the next steps are <command>xsetwacom "
"list dev</command>, <command>lsusb</command> and <command>xinput --list</"
"command>."
msgstr ""
"Zaznavanje <hardware>tablične naprave</hardware> poteka na več načinov. "
"<application>Solid</application> se uporablja v prvem koraku in podpira "
"hotplug. Če Solid ne uspe, so naslednji koraki <command>xsetwacom list dev</"
"command>, <command>lsusb</command> in <command>xinput --list</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should none of the commands above return the name of the tablet, it is not "
"supported and cannot be used by this module."
msgstr ""
"Če nobeden od zgornjih ukazov ne vrne imena tablice, ni podprta in je ta "
"modul ne more uporabljati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detection problems"
msgstr "Težave z odkrivanjem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the tablet is not detected check the <ulink url=\"https://linuxwacom."
"github.io\">&Linux; Wacom driver</ulink> or <ulink url=\"https://digimend."
"github.io\">DIGImend driver</ulink> page if your tablet is supported. "
"Furthermore check via <command>lsusb</command> if you can find your tablet."
msgstr ""
"Če tablični računalnik ni zaznan, preverite <ulink url=\"https://linuxwacom."
"github.io\">&Linux; Stran z gonilnikom Wacom</ulink> ali <ulink url="
"\"https://digimend.github.io\">gonilnik DIGImend</ulink>, če je vaš tablični "
"računalnik podprt. Prek <command>lsusb</command> preverite tudi, ali lahko "
"najdete svoj tablični računalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If udev does not handle the detection add the tablet to your <filename>/etc/"
"X11/xorg.conf.d/50-tablet.conf</filename> file (create it if it does not "
"exist) and restart the x-server."
msgstr ""
"Če udev ne obravnava zaznavanja, dodajte tablico v datoteko <filename>/etc/"
"X11/xorg.conf.d/50-tablet.conf</filename> (ustvarite jo, če ne obstaja) in "
"znova zaženite x- strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case of a serial device (Tablet PC and such) check if <command>xinput --"
"list</command> lists your input devices (Stylus/Eraser/Pad). Should they be "
"listed take a look at the internal tablet device id via <command>xsetwacom "
"get \"Name of your pad or stylus\" TabletID</command>. If an id is returned "
"please mail all the necessary information to the author."
msgstr ""
"V primeru serijske naprave (tablični računalnik in podobno) preverite, ali "
"<command>xinput --list</command> navaja vaše vnosne naprave (Stylus/Eraser/"
"Pad). Če so navedeni, si oglejte interni ID tablične naprave prek "
"<command>xsetwacom get \"Ime vaše ploščice ali pisala\" TabletID</command>. "
"Če je ID vrnjen, avtorju pošljite vse potrebne podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hotplug support is only available if the tablet is found via "
"<application>Solid</application> and its notification API."
msgstr ""
"Podpora za vročo priključitev je na voljo samo, če je tablični računalnik "
"najden prek <application>Solid</application> in njegovega API-ja za "
"obveščanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>Solid</application> checks if the value for the entry "
"<command>input.x11_options.Type</command> is <command>pen</command>, "
"<command>stylus</command>, <command>eraser</command> or <command>cursor</"
"command> or if the value for the entry <command>input.x11_driver</command> "
"is <command>wacom</command>."
msgstr ""
"<application>Solid</application> preveri, ali je vrednost za vnos "
"<command>input.x11_options.Type</command> <command>pero</command>, "
"<command>pisalo</command>, <command>radirka </command> ali <command>kurzor</"
"command> ali če je vrednost za vnos <command>input.x11_driver</command> "
"<command>wacom</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please mail the author if your tablet is detected by Solid but with other "
"values to enhance the tablet support."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo, pošljite e-pošto avtorju, če Solid zazna vaš tablični računalnik, "
"vendar z drugimi vrednostmi za izboljšanje podpore za tablični računalnik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tablet plasma applet"
msgstr "Plasma programček tablice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tablet applet makes it possible to change the available profiles on the "
"fly. Furthermore you can change the pad rotation and switch between absolute/"
"relative mode of the stylus/eraser regardless of the current profile "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Programček tabličnega računalnika omogoča sprotno spreminjanje "
"razpoložljivih profilov. Poleg tega lahko spreminjate vrtenje ploščice in "
"preklapljate med absolutnim/relativnim načinom pisala/radirke ne glede na "
"trenutne nastavitve profila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not necessary to add the plasmoid for this module to work. The default "
"profile will be activated by the <link linkend=\"kded\">tablet daemon</link> "
"as soon as it detects your tablet even if the plasmoid is not used. The "
"plasmoid is just a visual helper to switch easily between the profiles."
msgstr ""
"Za delovanje tega modula ni treba dodati plazmoida. Privzeti profil bo "
"aktiviral <link linkend=\"kded\">tablični demon</link> takoj, ko zazna vašo "
"tablico, tudi če plazmoida ne uporabljate. Plazmoid je le vizualni pomočnik "
"za enostavno preklapljanje med profili."

